Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.01,1:44:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, there are a lot of Fukei's attending.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.37,1:44:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.45,1:44:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So with that, this is Sakura Gakuin 2014 nendo.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.49,1:44:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to hand out the graduation diplomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.29,1:44:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, students, enter.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.79,1:45:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, graduates, enter
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.78,1:45:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bow!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.56,1:45:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.67,1:46:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Principal Kuramoto Mitsuru will hand out the graduation diplomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.89,1:46:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Elementary school, 6th grade, Okada Megumi
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.06,1:46:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hai!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.01,1:47:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Elementary school, 6th grade, Yamaide Aiko 
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.29,1:48:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, Jr High graduates.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.79,1:48:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Jr. High, 3rd year, Kikuchi Moa 
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.63,1:49:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Jr. High, 3rd year, Taguchi Hana 
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.51,1:50:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Jr. High, 3rd year, Notsu Yunano 
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.08,1:50:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jr. High, 3rd year, Mizuno Yui 
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.03,1:51:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, to give the student's Souji [a speech given to the graduates, showing appreciation and congratulations]
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.07,1:51:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura Gakuin, entrance year 2011, Jr High, 2nd year, Rinon Isono
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.47,2:00:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, to give the Graduation Toji
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.04,2:00:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura Gakuin, Jr. High 3rd year.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.25,2:00:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hai!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.20,2:00:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To be represented by Student Council President Moa Kikuchi.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:26.39,2:11:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Sakura Gakuin Principal Kuramoto will give a Shukuji [a celebratory speech]
Dialogue: 0,2:19:39.88,2:19:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, let me say a few words, excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,2:19:48.59,2:19:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, to all watching the live stream, it is now your chance for a bathroom break.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:53.70,2:19:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go now. For those here, please stay.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:57.94,2:20:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I see it in the corner of my eye, my ego may bruise.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:01.74,2:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so let me say my honest thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:07.75,2:20:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... this year, I was really worried about these four graduates.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:14.44,2:20:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As some may already know,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:17.42,2:20:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,when I banter, there is one who cries easily.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:22.73,2:20:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're performing live, and they lost the will to fight.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:27.77,2:20:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was over enthusiastic, there was one who would shut down emotionally.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:32.87,2:20:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One who was proud of her impersonations, who would leave the audience at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:38.04,2:20:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Truthfully... my job is to MC, in the role of a teacher,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:44.88,2:20:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was really worried this year.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:47.25,2:20:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But the year has passed. 
Dialogue: 0,2:20:49.22,2:20:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially in these few months, these four can now be on stage and say what they want. 
Dialogue: 0,2:20:57.02,2:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,During the liver performances they respond and started bantering back.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:02.13,2:21:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say it.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:04.57,2:21:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:07.37,2:21:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I say this...
Dialogue: 0,2:21:09.67,2:21:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think a lot of you may have not been comfortable with my banter.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:14.51,2:21:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But you gained the courage and stepped up.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:21.15,2:21:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, to me that is my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:25.39,2:21:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know, every year, just as it is getting fun, we come to the graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:35.80,2:21:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My emotional milk crepe is all limp and floppy.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:46.91,2:21:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So as a teacher, I thought about this very hard, and came up with this.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:54.16,2:21:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So I know formally that you are all graduating.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:58.69,2:22:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But in my heart, you are all held back a year.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:04.80,2:22:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I need to face the music,
Dialogue: 0,2:22:08.43,2:22:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am worried about all of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:12.00,2:22:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:13.84,2:22:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sure the Fukei's understand...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:16.11,2:22:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as all of the staff.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:18.21,2:22:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are ever in trouble we will all come to your aid.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:21.62,2:22:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even after you graduate, I'll still be your teacher, 
Dialogue: 0,2:22:29.14,2:22:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll still banter and bring out your individual charm...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:34.20,2:22:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can have that kind of relationship.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:37.36,2:22:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what I feel.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:39.56,2:22:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course this applies to all the previous graduates as well.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:45.84,2:22:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I still watch the "Merengue no Kimochi" with butterflies in my stomach,
Dialogue: 0,2:22:55.95,2:22:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know. So, I want you to rely on me.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:59.08,2:23:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Although if the Nurse comes to depend on me, I'm not sure what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:03.25,2:23:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So in my mind, all of you,
Dialogue: 0,2:23:10.26,2:23:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have not put the seal of approval on your graduation certificate in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:16.30,2:23:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, right now,
Dialogue: 0,2:23:19.40,2:23:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,they say you are all grown up... but you carry a lot on your little shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:23.71,2:23:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The weight you carry...
Dialogue: 0,2:23:27.18,2:23:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I sometimes feel that you should share that burden.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:31.98,2:23:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure a lot of people feel the same way... I know staff does.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:35.42,2:23:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I am saying things, still holding on to you…
Dialogue: 0,2:23:42.26,2:23:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So what I want to really say is "Let me still act as your teacher", that is all.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:50.83,2:23:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So with that, congratulations on your graduation. 
Dialogue: 0,2:23:54.18,2:23:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please remember me…
Dialogue: 0,2:24:07.02,2:24:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So with that, I'm sorry it's always me speaking last.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:12.45,2:24:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come back from your bathroom break?\N Everyone in the live viewing?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:16.46,2:24:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Truthfully, I derailed the conversation, but…
Dialogue: 0,2:24:21.37,2:24:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... so with this, we're going to perform now...
Dialogue: 0,2:24:26.20,2:24:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, all the tears stopped flowing!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:30.07,2:24:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my intention.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:32.11,2:24:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So go back and change,
Dialogue: 0,2:24:35.25,2:24:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,entertain the Fukei-san till the very end!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:40.42,2:24:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...\NGraduating Class, you are dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:45.52,2:24:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please give a round of applause.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:20.72,2:25:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, the 2014 Graduation Ceremony has ended.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:27.73,2:25:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone bow.
